These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-1::.
City: nizza, marseilles
There 2 different types of food: garlic, spinach
There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, black
1. the person eating garlic is not to the left of the person who likes emerald##8
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| City         | marseilles   | nizza |
| Food   | garlic | spinach    |
| Color     | emerald  | black |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, mystery
2 different games are played: go, poker
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, green
1. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes amber is not to the right of the person playing go##8
3. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Movie-Genre      | mystery    | horror    |
| Game   | go | poker    |
| Color     | amber  | green |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, basketball
City: rome, marseilles
2 different pets are kept: ferret, cat
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
2. the person traveling to marseilles is not the owner of the cat##6
3. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |        2        |
| Sport      | biathlon   | basketball           |
| City           | rome | marseilles |
| Pet   | cat  | ferret      |

