.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice
There 2 different types of food: plum, orange
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, roller
1. the person eating plum is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage         | soy-milk | juice    |
| Food           | plum  | orange |
| Transport   | skateboard      | roller    |

