.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-10::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, martial-arts
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, may
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep
1. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##8
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |  2   |
| Movie-Genre        | martial-arts | romance |
| Birthday         | may     | july |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | ambient  |

